title: Grateful Dead Live at Henry J. Kaiser Convention Center on 1986-12-30
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket
Althea
C.C. Rider

My Brother Esau

Set 2

Eyes Of The World

Ollin Arageed *

William Green - Drums #
